{"tid":1351113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[跣佢老母] 齊齊聯署+email去英國褫奪何君妖博士學位","createTime":"2019-07-22T14:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T12:09:45.000Z","uid":279268,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"e070b26e0b9ba9ec5a849351df293c6c8e5f8463","tid":1351113,"uid":279268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:37:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">眾新聞:<br />\n// 何君堯今日已成APU傑出校友。他在2011年，獲APU頒授榮譽法律博士學位。APU其後何君堯的履歷中，除了回顧律師會工作，也讚揚他的成就之一，是發起反佔中「保衛中環」運動 //</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">麻煩大家幫手 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1) 簽爆個聯署</span>, 再加 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2) send email去大學</span><br />\n唔好再畀何君率眾妖害人， 擾亂香港安寧！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">1) 聯署:</span></span><br />\n強烈要求英國Anglia Ruskin大學同校長Roderick Watkins重新審視同何君堯既關係，<br />\n並且撤銷佢既榮譽博士學位 <br />\n<a href=\"http://chng.it/CdhBgdYtjZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2FCdhBgdYtjZ&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=f529cbf8\" target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/CdhBgdYtjZ</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">2) Send Email</span></span>:<br />\nEmail 主旨: Complaint about Honorary Doctor, Junius Ho <br />\n收件者 (send晒去三個email啦)<br />\n校長 VC: <br />\nroderick.watkins@anglia.ac.uk<br />\n高級新聞主任 Senior Press Officer: <br />\njon.green@anglia.ac.uk<br />\n投訴部 email: <br />\ncomplaints@anglia.ac.uk<br />\n<br />\nDear Vice-Chancellor Roderick Watkins and the Press Office for Anglia Ruskin University, <br />\n<br />\nI am a Hong Kong citizen, writing to bring to your attention the recent disgraceful conduct of your Honorary Doctoral Award recipient and &ldquo;ambassador&rdquo;, Junius Ho (1). <br />\n<br />\nWe trust you will want to be aware of any circumstances that may cause you to reconsider whether Junius Ho is, as you describe, an &ldquo;outstanding ambassador for Anglia Ruskin University in Hong Kong&rdquo;, and whether he deserves the university&rsquo;s continuing endorsement as an &lsquo;Honorary Doctor&rsquo;.  <br />\n<br />\nIn September 2017, Junius Ho called for pro-independence protesters in Hong Kong to be killed &quot;without mercy&quot; (2). He also said that &quot;it was no big deal to kill pigs or dogs&quot;. This was widely criticised, accused of being &lsquo;incitement to violence&rsquo;, and condemned even by the Hong Kong Chief Executive. Junius Ho showed no remorse. <br />\n<br />\nJunius Ho has been a vocal critic of the ongoing protests against a proposed Hong Kong extradition bill. On July 15th, he published a series of photos of ordinary western citizens taken around Hong Kong, claiming that they were US spies (without providing any evidence). This placed these individuals at serious risk of being targeted by his supporters. <br />\n<br />\nOn the evening of Sunday 21st July, a gang of 200 to 300 men with weapons brutally beat defenceless commuters, some of whom had been at the anti-extradition demonstrations earlier that day, as they disembarked a train in Yuen Long station. 36 of the victims were hospitalised, with those hurt including journalists and a pregnant woman. Footage shows Junius Ho shaking hands with and congratulating several of the attackers during the evening, giving them a thumbs-up and applause, and calling them &quot;heroes&quot;. While Ho denies that he knew the men, or supported their violence, his presence at the scene has today made him the subject of serious accusations and calls for an investigation. <br />\n<br />\nIf Junius Ho had done only one of these things, it would seem like behaviour that the university would want to distance itself from. But in light of his ongoing statements and behaviour leading up to the horrific events of Sunday 21st July, I strongly urge you to reconsider your endorsement of Junius Ho and revoke the Honorary Doctoral Award. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://aru.ac.uk/graduation-and-alumni/honorary-award-holders2/junius-ho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faru.ac.uk%2Fgraduation-and-alumni%2Fhonorary-award-holders2%2Fjunius-ho&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=5eab2771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://aru.ac.uk/graduation-and-alumni/honorary-award-holders2/junius-ho</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/2114300/lawmaker-junius-ho-face-probe-over-call-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F2114300%2Flawmaker-junius-ho-face-probe-over-call-hong-kong&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=006ca703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/2114300/lawmaker-junius-ho-face-probe-over-call-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\nYours sincerely, <br />\nXX[加你個名]XX<br />\nHong Kong Citizen<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果冷血對待香港市民，係「先撩者賤」！</span><br />\nSHARE 出去呀！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FMpSbW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFMpSbW4.jpg&h=11d466ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R8MdFRf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR8MdFRf.jpg&h=59e46125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qq8Pebf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqq8Pebf.jpg&h=7cf8111e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13039fc727ec04255a2289a9da3c77fad6e23928","tid":1351113,"uid":258010,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:42:41.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n跣走個學位<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">執葉呀拿</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a7bb6cc42ea5f281b514fd2571f1decd03234cc","tid":1351113,"uid":279268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:46:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">何君堯 ARU | Anglia Ruskin University</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://aru.ac.uk/graduation-and-alumni/honorary-award-holders2/junius-ho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faru.ac.uk%2Fgraduation-and-alumni%2Fhonorary-award-holders2%2Fjunius-ho&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=5eab2771\" target=\"_blank\">https://aru.ac.uk/graduation-and-alumni/honorary-award-holders2/junius-ho</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/soaqw3Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsoaqw3Y.png&h=52b5027c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">立場新聞: 何君堯獲「榮譽法學博士」學位？</span><br />\n//但何聲稱自己是「榮譽」法學博士，就是要別人以為他這個讀書差勁的人是真正的法學博士了，而且很厲害，有honours的。比起非執業而冒稱執業，這個冒牌「法學博士」情節嚴重得多了。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%A6%AE%E8%AD%BD%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%B8%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB-%E5%AD%B8%E4%BD%8D-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E5%90%8C%E5%BF%97%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E8%99%9B%E5%81%87%E9%99%B3%E8%BF%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E8%25AD%25BD%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%258D%259A%25E5%25A3%25AB-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E4%25BD%258D-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25BF%2597%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258F%25A6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2599%259B%25E5%2581%2587%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%25BF%25B0%2F&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=38133c82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E8%25AD%25BD%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%258D%259A%25E5%25A3%25AB-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E4%25BD%258D-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25BF%2597%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258F%25A6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2599%259B%25E5%2581%2587%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%25BF%25B0%2F&h=9721273b\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%A6%AE%E8%AD%BD%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%B8%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB-%E5%AD%B8%E4%BD%8D-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E5%90%8C%E5%BF%97%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E8%99%9B%E5%81%87%E9%99%B3%E8%BF%B0/</a><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: green;\">眾新聞: 何君堯憶年少輕狂：攤大手板用老豆錢、追女致重讀PCLL</span><br />\n//何君堯的求學史，還有一個未解之謎。翻查APU年鑑， 何君堯1984年APU法律學士剛剛畢業，同年已向州瑪高等教育學院捐款，金額不詳。在八十年代， APU每年平均有3至5名校友捐款，當年無工作、靠父親供養的何君堯已是其中一人。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/7128/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-%E5%9F%B7%E6%A5%AD%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-7129/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E6%86%B6%E5%B9%B4%E5%B0%91%E8%BC%95%E7%8B%82%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%A4%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%8B%E6%9D%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%81%E8%B1%86%E9%8C%A2%E3%80%81%E8%BF%BD%E5%A5%B3%E8%87%B4%E9%87%8D%E8%AE%80pcll\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F7128%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF-%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B-7129%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E6%2586%25B6%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25B0%2591%25E8%25BC%2595%25E7%258B%2582%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2594%25A4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%259D%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%2580%2581%25E8%25B1%2586%25E9%258C%25A2%25E3%2580%2581%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%2587%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25AE%2580pcll&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=bbfa7370\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/7128/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-%E5%9F%B7%E6%A5%AD%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-7129/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E6%86%B6%E5%B9%B4%E5%B0%91%E8%BC%95%E7%8B%82%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%A4%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%8B%E6%9D%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%81%E8%B1%86%E9%8C%A2%E3%80%81%E8%BF%BD%E5%A5%B3%E8%87%B4%E9%87%8D%E8%AE%80pcll</a>"},{"pid":"c8e4369daf52f04555a150daec67e8306bf525f1","tid":1351113,"uid":279